reviewText: The best buy I ever made in years Season 3 -4 of the Martin Comedy Series, I remember as a kid watching and loving this show on Friday nights. Thw whole cast is amaxing, Gina, Tommy, Cole and Pam, each of them make the show the #1 success it was. I can watch these DVD;s over and over again, thats the wonderful thing about comedy. Man the best buy I ever bought, Wazup, QWaz Up, WAAAz Uuuup!
